@startuml
title Plane State Transition Diagram

state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state "Out of Service"
state "Removed from Service"

[*] --> Order

Order --> Arrival : Plane acquired

Arrival --> Preparation : Arrival at base

Preparation --> Operations : Ready for operations
Preparation --> Maintenance : Needs maintenance

Operations --> Maintenance : No more flights or maintenance required

Maintenance --> Preparation : Maintenance completed

Operations --> "Out of Service" : Plane unavailable

"Out of Service" --> "Removed from Service" : Permanently withdrawn

@enduml
